 <span data-ttu-id="5b148-123"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedAudio.StartTime%2A> Свойство получает системное время в начале операции распознавания.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b148-123">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedAudio.StartTime%2A> property gets the system time at the start of the recognition operation.</span></span>  
  
   
  
